<L>__{int day: neri's apt. (1955)}
<A>__{albert neri moves around in his small corona apartment; he pulls a small trunk from under his bed. he opens it, and we see in it, nearly folded, a new york city policeman's uniform. he takes it out piece by piece, almost reverently. then the badge, and the identification card; with his picture on it. slowly, in the solitude of his room, he begins to dress.}
